    "description": "Edge-Based Autonomous Control Platform for AI-Era Data Center Energy Optimization\n\nDesigned an innovative platform leveraging edge NPU gateways and multi-agentic frameworks to autonomously control data center power/cooling infrastructure in real-time.\n\nThe solution targets PUE improvement of 0.02p+, 3-5% power reduction, and 5-10% cooling efficiency gains, achieving 20% reduction in unplanned downtime through ultra-low latency control (<50ms) and predictive maintenance."
  },
